org.springframework.data.gemfire.repository.query.support

Enum OqlKeyword

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<OqlKeyword>
      • org.springframework.data.gemfire.repository.query.support.OqlKeyword
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<OqlKeyword>

    public enum OqlKeyword
extends java.lang.Enum<OqlKeyword>
    The OqlKeyword enum represents the complete set of keywords (Reserved Words) in Apache Geode's Object Query Language (OQL).
    Since:
    1.0.0
    See Also:
    Supported Keywords
